results.title: Torment, Part 4
results.description: Is Kraven back from the dead?  If so, how has he resurrected himself?  With Spidey, the Lizard, Kraven, and the mystery villain, you can bet that Spider-Man won't by lying in the garbage through that meeting. [per next issue box]

results.title: Light the Night!, Part Three
results.description: Electro's ultimate scheme backfires, leaving him asking Spider-Man for help

results.title: Storm Warnings, Part One
results.description: Iron Fist steals Kate Cushing's A.R.M.S. research to uncover a traitor in his corporation

results.title: Lock and Load (Storm Warnings, Part 2)
results.description: While Spider-Man and Iron Fist fight the first Platoon atop the Brooklyn Bridge, A.R.M.S. prepares for a full-scale field demonstration of the Platoon armor

results.title: Media Blitz (Storm Warnings, Part 3)
results.description: Spider-Man and Iron Fist try to prevent the Platoons from reaching Brooklyn

results.title: The Anniversary Syndrome
results.description: Spider-Man commemorates an important anniversary by stopping a gang of drug dealers under the protection of the Hobgoblin

results.title: The Dream Before (Pursuit, Part One)
results.description: Spider-Man, furious over the loss of what he thought were his parents, scours the city for the man responsible -- the Chameleon

results.title: Directions (Beware the Rage of a Desperate Man!, Chapter 1)
results.description: Spider-Man intervenes in a fight between Demogoblin and Jason Macendale in the mansion of the late Kraven

results.title: Old Habits ... (Beware the Rage of a Desperate Man!, Chapter 2)
results.description: Spider-Man tries to stop Demogoblin's escape from prison; Jason Macendale makes a deal with the son of Kraven the Hunter

results.title: Demons of Our Past (Beware the Rage of a Desperate Man!, Chapter 3)
results.description: Hobgoblin returns to the United States with new powers and confronts the Demogoblin

results.title: Cold Hearts (Beware the Rage of a Desperate Man!, Conclusion)
results.description: Spider-Man, determined to stop the Hobgoblin, is met by the misguided resistance of Coldheart; Vladimir Kravinoff seeks his father's enhanced abilities

results.title: Torment, Part 5
results.description: Is Spider-Man dead?  Of course not, but he's not in very good shape. [per next issue box]

results.title: Masques, Part 1
results.description: Hobgoblin kidnaps a child and it's up to Spider-Man and the Spirit of Vengeance to catch him.

results.title: Masques, Part 2
results.description: Spidey and Ghost Rider rescue Adam from the Hobgoblin.

items.name: But Not on an actual published Comic

results.title: The Night of the Goblin! (Revelations, Part 4)
results.description: The Spider-Clone storyline ends with a climactic battle Peter Parker and the mastermind behind the affair, Norman Osborn

results.title: SHOC
results.description: Spider-Man meets a new hero, SHOC, who helps him against a new villain, Crown; Peter and Mary Jane sign up for classes at Empire State University

results.title: The Vampire's Kiss
results.description: Spider-Man searches the ESU campus for Morbius, while Morbius searches for a possible cure; Morbius bites Spider-Man

results.title: The Love of a Woman
results.description: Spider-Man, still ill from Morbius' bite, attempts to find the vampire before he kills again

results.title: After the Fall
results.description: Dr. Janson delivers Morbius into the hands of Crown and HYDRA; Peter Parker becomes embroiled in the battle between HYDRA and SHOC

results.title: Blood Simple
results.description: Hammerhead rescues Peter Parker and SHOC from HYDRA, then enlists SHOC's aid against Fortunato ... but Crown and HYDRA find them first

results.title: Shadow of the Cat
results.description: Spider-Man helps Cat find his son's kidnappers

results.title: You've Got to Have Friends (of Humanity?)
results.description: Spider-Man intervenes when a riot breaks out at a Friends of Humanity rally on the ESU campus; the effects of Morbius' bite on Spider-Man become more pronounced

results.title: Vertigo
results.description: Spider-Man, suffering from vertigo induced by Morbius' bite, clings for his life to the side of a skyscraper; Robin Vega forces Paul Stacy to reconsider joining the Friends of Humanity

results.title: Nothing Stops the Juggernaut!
results.description: The Juggernaut, in New York City to deliver a sword to his employers (see Incredible Hulk #457), picks a fight with Spider-Man

results.title: Little Lies
results.description: Donovan Zane sends the Shocker to kill Paul Stacy

results.title: The Span of Years
results.description: Spider-Man fights the Shocker atop the Brokklyn Bridge to save the life of Paul Stacy
